<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA23">
<l>tāḻntuvaraṅ koṇṭu takka vakaikaḷāl</l>
<l>vāḻntu kaḻivārai vāḻvikkun – tāḻnta</l>
<l>viḷaṅkaṉikkuk kaṉṟeṟintu vēṟṟuruvāy ñāla</l>
<l>maḷantaṭikkīḻk koṇṭa vavaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will let live those who pass [their] time bowing low,</l>
<l>taking boons, living in befitting ways,</l>
<l>he who threw the calf onto the hanging wood-apple fruits [and], in another form,</l>
<l>measured the world [and] took it under [his] foot.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
